dc_description_s: This polygon shapefile was derived from the National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration Coastal Change Analysis Program's Southern Coastal California Land Cover data. It depicts coastal marshes in Santa Barbara, Ventura, Los Angeles, San Bernardino, Orange, Riverside and San Diego counties.This coverage includes California counties represented by the MLPA South Coast Study Region, from Point Conception south to the Mexico border.
